window.bookSummaryJSON = "From the #1 <i>New York Times</i> bestselling author of <i>Words of Radiance</i>, co-author of Robert Jordan's Wheel of Time series and creator of the internationally bestselling Mistborn Trilogy, Brandon Sanderson, comes <i>Mitosis</i>, a short story set in the action-packed world of <i>Steelheart</i>: the Reckoners series, exclusively available in a HB collector's edition. Epics still plague Newcago, but David and the Reckoners have vowed to fight back. Catch all the action before <i>Firefight,</i> the exciting sequel to <i>Steelheart</i>, hits the shelves."; 
